body.description: The SanDisk Ultra Flair USB 3.0 flash drive moves your files fast. Spend less time waiting to transfer files and enjoy high-speed USB 3.0 performance of up to 150MB/s. With transfer speeds to drive up to 15 times faster than standard USB 2.0 drives, you can transfer a full length movie in less than 30 seconds. Its durable and sleek metal casing is tough enough to handle knocks with style. And, with password protection, you can rest assured that your private files stay private. Help secure files in style with the SanDisk Ultra Flair USB 3.0 flash drive.

reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Reliable and High-Speed Storage on the Go with SanDisk Ultra Flair!
reviews.reviewText: Rating: ⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐The SanDisk 128GB Ultra Flair USB 3.0 Flash Drive is a sleek and dependable solution for storing and transferring your data with ease.Pros: 1. Ample Storage: With 128GB of storage capacity, this flash drive offers plenty of space to store a wide range of files, from documents and photos to videos and music. 2. High-Speed USB 3.0: The USB 3.0 interface provides lightning-fast data transfer speeds, significantly reducing the time it takes to copy large files. It’s backward compatible with USB 2.0, ensuring compatibility with a wide range of devices. 3. Durable and Stylish: The metal casing not only gives the drive a stylish and modern look but also provides durability and protection for your data. 4. Compact and Portable: The small and lightweight design of the Ultra Flair allows you to take it with you wherever you go. It’s an ideal solution for students, professionals, and anyone who needs to carry their data on the go. 5. Reliable Brand: SanDisk is a trusted name in the world of flash storage. You can count on the quality and reliability of their products.Cons: 1. Cap Protection: While the drive is durable and reliable, it lacks a cap or cover to protect the USB connector. This isn’t a significant issue, but it’s worth noting if you’re concerned about potential damage to the connector.In summary, the SanDisk 128GB Ultra Flair USB 3.0 Flash Drive is a reliable and high-speed storage solution that’s perfect for anyone in need of portable data storage. With ample storage capacity and fast transfer speeds, it’s an excellent choice for students, professionals, and anyone who wants to carry their files in their pocket. While it lacks a cap for the USB connector, the drive’s durability and performance make it a top-notch option for on-the-go data needs. Highly recommended!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 18, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Sandisk 128 GB Flair ... good price ... good performance
reviews.reviewText: Device smaller than I thought it would be. Sequential read and write is quite good. Random read and write good. Summary below, on Win11 system, using CrystalDiskMark 8.04 (x64):Sequential Read Average: 160 MB/sSequential Write Average: 68 MB/sRandom Read Average: 9 MB/sRandom Write Average: 2.5 MB/sIn comparison, these are the benchmarks for a Sandisk 32GB flash drive:Sequential Read Average: 160 MB/sSequential Write Average: 47 MB/sRandom Read Average: 7 MB/sRandom Write Average: 1.5 MB/sSo it performed slightly better on random read/writes, but much better on sequential reads. Advertised speeds are usually for sequential operations. If you are writing a lot of small files in one operation, write speeds will be slower since system has to write entries in the directory for each file, reducing overall throughput.The drive did get a bit warm (not hot, but noticeably warm) after running the benchmarks, but the case is metal, and if it was encased in plastic, as many other flash drives, one might not notice. I guess having exposed metal case helps with cooling. Will have to see how it holds up to writing a full 2 hour movie.All tests were done on new, freshly formatted (e.g. empty) flash drives.So in summary, its a decent drive. Noting to 'write home about' but the price was decent.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 1, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Great for the most part, beware fragile casing
reviews.reviewText: These offer a fantastic tradeoff between size, storage, and portability. USB 3.0 support is a nice plus, especially if you want to use these for live CDs. They seem to have a strange failure mechanism however, which is a fragile area around the plastic "ring" in the casing. I am now more gentle with insertion/removal and haven't recreated the failure mechanism since, so it is difficult to know if this is a common point-of-failure or a one-time fluke. I'd recommend handling these carefully.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 26, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars This is an Impressive Flash Drive.
reviews.reviewText: Too many times I have lost all of my data on my computer and have had to reset it to a factory condition, wishing that I had backed up my data before the incident. Now, with the SanDisk 16GB Ultra Flair USB 3.0 Flash Drive, I have no more concerns about losing data from a crash or virus incident. I'm confident that the Disk is going to do what it says it will because I checked the backup files on the flash drive and found them all intact and usable.I hope that I never really have to use the flash drive, but I'm not concerned about the possibility of a crash or virus infection, because I have all of my files backed up on the drive.The only issue I have with the flash drive is how small it is. I appreciate the technology to make the drive small and efficient, but I am prone to losing things for various reasons. Thus, I would prefer it to be a little larger, making it easier to find. Just for thought, maybe it can be constructed in bright colors to make it easier to see and find. Otherwise, it is a good buy for the price and performs exceptionally. I recommend the SanDisk 16GB Ultra Flair USB 3.0 Flash Drive for backup and storage of data.

reviews.reviewTitle: Swift and Secure Data Storage: SanDisk Ultra Flair USB 3.0 128GB Flash Drive
reviews.reviewText: The SanDisk Ultra Flair USB 3.0 128GB Flash Drive has truly impressed me with its exceptional performance and reliability, and I'm delighted to give it a solid five-star rating. This compact yet high-capacity flash drive has become an essential part of my digital life.From the very first use, the SanDisk Ultra Flair proved its worth with its impressive data transfer speed. With up to 150MB/s read performance, transferring large files and media is a breeze. This flash drive has saved me valuable time when moving data between devices or sharing files with friends and colleagues.The sleek black and silver design adds a touch of sophistication to the flash drive. The durable metal casing not only protects the drive but also adds to its premium feel. It's clear that SanDisk prioritizes both functionality and aesthetics in their design.The USB 3.0 technology ensures compatibility with various devices, and the backward compatibility with USB 2.0 ensures that I can use the flash drive across a wide range of devices, old and new. This versatility is a significant advantage for those who need to transfer data between different systems.The SanDisk brand is synonymous with reliability, and the Ultra Flair flash drive is no exception. The drive's build quality feels solid, and the metal casing provides an added layer of protection against everyday wear and tear. I trust this flash drive to safely store and transport my important files.The 128GB storage capacity is generous enough to accommodate a wide range of files, whether it's documents, photos, videos, or multimedia projects. Its compact size allows me to carry a significant amount of data in my pocket, making it an ideal solution for work, school, and entertainment.In conclusion, the SanDisk Ultra Flair USB 3.0 128GB Flash Drive is a five-star digital storage solution that delivers on both speed and security. Its impressive performance, sleek design, and durability make it an essential accessory for anyone seeking reliable data storage and transfer capabilities. If you're looking for a high-performance flash drive that combines functionality with style, the SanDisk Ultra Flair is the perfect choice that has earned its five-star rating with flying colors.
